Living alone in a flat outside the old town
Claire is a French girl who has been living in Barcelona for 5 years. She moved to study a Master
in Communication and Journalism and decided to stay. Now she works as a clerk in a clothing
store to be able to pay the rent and her expenses. She shares a flat with two friends in a quiet
street in the Born. She likes to party with her friends, especially going to events like concerts
and festivals. She loves documentaries and movies but don't like to go to the cinema. She hates
the public transport but she has to take the metro to go to work. She's goes to the gym because
she likes to take care of herself and keep in shape.
